# API Rules

- [base.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/base.mdc)

## Stack

- Node.js
- Pothos (GraphQL schema builder)
- GraphQL Yoga
- Prisma (database ORM)
- Gql.tada

## Guidelines

- Follow backend patterns consistent with Pothos schema builder and GraphQL Yoga server.
- Use Prisma for all database access.
